Welding Inspector (Contract)
Responsibilities
To perform welding inspection according to the approved standard specifications and international standardsTo collect the variances taking place in welding works, and able to advise the corrective action  Requirements: Minimum education SMA/STMHave welding inspector certificate from BNSP/B4T Bandung/LSP Migas/well recognized certification institutionAt least 3 year(s) of working experience in welding inspection in various projects, preferred in tank project experienceHaving strong knowledge of welding procedures, welding metallurgy, NDT testsAbility to read engineering drawingsable to work in a team and able to drive the contractors' construction workers
